tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE weather_data (
  date DATE,
  time TIME,
  temperature FLOAT,
  air_pressure FLOAT,
  wind_speed FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE location (
  location_id INT,
  city VARCHAR(50),
  country VARCHAR(50),
  longitude FLOAT,
  latitude FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE energy_production (
  date DATE,
  time TIME,
  location_id INT,
  wind_speed FLOAT,
  power_generated FLOAT
);
